<subSubSection id="A8D0653DFF0CFF695889F882FAB86064" lastPageId="194" lastPageNumber="195" pageId="193" pageNumber="194" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="E07536B6FF0CFF695889F882FAB86064" blockId="193.[151,1437,1590,2013]" lastBlockId="194.[199,1436,151,285]" lastPageId="194" lastPageNumber="195" pageId="193" pageNumber="194">
REMARKS: 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF0CFF6A590EF883FDA26650" author="Rondani, C." box="[272,529,1806,1833]" pageId="193" pageNumber="194" pagination="1" refId="ref368514" refString="Rondani, C. (1859 b) Dipterologiae italicae prodromus. Vol: III. Species italicae ordinis dipterorum in genera characteribus definita, ordinatim collectae, methodo analitica distinctae, et novis vel minus cognitis descriptis. Pars secunda: Muscidae, Siphoninae et (partim) Tachininae. A. Stocchi, Parmae [= Parma], 243 + [1] p., 1 pl." type="journal article" year="1859">Rondani (1859b: 206)</bibRefCitation>
proposed 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FF0CFF6A5A8EF883FCAD6651" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1859" box="[656,798,1806,1832]" class="Insecta" family="Sarcophagidae" genus="Mesomelena" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="193" pageNumber="194" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FF0CFF6A5A8EF883FCAD6651" box="[656,798,1806,1832]" italics="true" pageId="193" pageNumber="194">Mesomelena</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a new genus and identified 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FF0CFF6A5C84F882FEFF6635" authority="Loew, 1848" authorityName="Loew" authorityYear="1848" class="Insecta" family="Sarcophagidae" genus="Metopia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="193" pageNumber="194" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mesomelaena">
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FF0CFF6A5C84F882FA2F6651" box="[1178,1436,1806,1832]" italics="true" pageId="193" pageNumber="194">Metopia mesomelaena</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF0CFF6A58D9F8BEFEFF6635" author="Loew, H." box="[199,332,1842,1869]" pageId="193" pageNumber="194" pagination="377 - 378" refId="ref356490" refString="Loew, H. (1848) Eine neue europaische Art der Gattung Metopia. Entomologische Zeitung, 9, 377 - 378." type="journal article" year="1848">Loew, 1848</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
as the 
<typeStatus id="3F718814FF0CFF6A5980F8BEFE7D6634" box="[414,462,1843,1869]" pageId="193" pageNumber="194">type</typeStatus>
species. Having used the species epithet for the new nominal genus and thinking that 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FF0CFF6A58D9F8DBFE466609" baseAuthorityName="Loew" baseAuthorityYear="1848" box="[199,501,1878,1904]" class="Insecta" family="Sarcophagidae" genus="Mesomelena" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="193" pageNumber="194" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mesomelaena">
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FF0CFF6A58D9F8DBFE466609" box="[199,501,1878,1904]" italics="true" pageId="193" pageNumber="194">Mesomelena mesomelaena</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was incorrect, Rondani incorrectly substituted it with 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FF0CFF6A5C40F8DBFA846609" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1859" box="[1118,1335,1878,1904]" class="Insecta" family="Sarcophagidae" genus="Mesomelena" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="193" pageNumber="194" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="loewii">
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FF0CFF6A5C40F8DBFA846609" box="[1118,1335,1878,1904]" italics="true" pageId="193" pageNumber="194">Mesomelena loewii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF0CFF6A5D59F8DBFEED66EC" author="Schiner, I. R." pageId="193" pageNumber="194" pagination="441 - 656" refId="ref372602" refString="Schiner, I. R. (1861 b) Fauna Austriaca. Die Fliegen (Diptera). Nach der analytischen Methode bearbeitet, mit der Characteristik sammtlicher europaischer Gattungen, der Beschreibung aller in Deutschland vorkommenden Arten und der Aufzahlung aller bisher beschriebene europaischen Arten. I. Theil. [Heft 6 / 7]. C. Gerold's Sohn, Wien, pp. 441 - 656. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 8525" type="book chapter" year="1861">Schiner (1861b: 501)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF0CFF6A5973F8F7FD1266EC" author="Bezzi, M. &amp; Stein, P." box="[365,673,1914,1941]" pageId="193" pageNumber="194" pagination="1 - 747" refId="ref346041" refString="Bezzi, M. &amp; Stein, P. (1907) Cyclorrapha Aschiza. Cyclorrapha Schizophora: Schizometopa. In: Becker, T., Bezzi, M., Kertesz, K. &amp; Stein, P. (Eds.), Katalog der palaarktischen Dipteren. Band III. G. Wesselenyi in Hodmezovasarhely, Budapest, pp. 1 - 747." type="book chapter" year="1907">Bezzi &amp; Stein (1907: 515)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF0CFF6A5AC0F8F7FC4666EC" author="Rohdendorf, B." box="[734,1013,1914,1941]" pageId="193" pageNumber="194" pagination="177 - 232" refId="ref366661" refString="Rohdendorf, B. (1975) 64 h. Sarcophaginae. In: Lindner, E. (Ed.), Die Fliegen der Palaearktischen Region. Band XI. Lieferung. 311. E. Schweizerbart, Stuttgart, pp. 177 - 232." type="book chapter" year="1975">Rohdendorf (1975: 186)</bibRefCitation>
placed this name in synonymy with 
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FF0CFF6A58D9F813FE4A66C1" box="[199,505,1950,1976]" italics="true" pageId="193" pageNumber="194">
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FF0CFF6A58D9F813FE4666C1" baseAuthorityName="Loew" baseAuthorityYear="1848" box="[199,501,1950,1976]" class="Insecta" family="Sarcophagidae" genus="Mesomelena" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="193" pageNumber="194" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mesomelaena">Mesomelena mesomelaena</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
while 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF0CFF6A5A5CF812FC6366C1" author="Brauer, F. &amp; Bergenstamm, J. E. von" box="[578,976,1950,1977]" pageId="193" pageNumber="194" pagination="69 - 180" refId="ref346619" refString="Brauer, F. &amp; Bergenstamm, J. E. von (1889) Die Zweiflugler der Kaiserlichen Museums zu Wien. IV. Vorarbeiten zu einer Monographie der Muscaria Schizometopa (exclusive Anthomyidae). Pars I. Denkschriften der Kaiserlichen Akademie der Wissenschaften. Wien. Mathematisch-Naturwissenschaftliche Classe, 56 (1), 69 - 180, 11 pls." type="journal article" year="1889">Brauer &amp; Bergenstamm (1889: 178)</bibRefCitation>
considered it as a valid species. The 
<typeStatus id="3F718814FF0CFF6A5D7FF812FA2F66C0" box="[1377,1436,1951,1977]" pageId="193" pageNumber="194">types</typeStatus>
for 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FF0CFF6A58F0F84EFE2566A5" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1859" box="[238,406,1986,2012]" class="Insecta" family="Sarcophagidae" genus="Metopia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="193" pageNumber="194" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="loewii">
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FF0CFF6A58F0F84EFE2566A5" box="[238,406,1986,2012]" italics="true" pageId="193" pageNumber="194">Metopia loewii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
will be the same as for the name it was proposed to replace, i.e., 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FF0CFF6A5C77F84FFA2666A5" baseAuthorityName="Loew" baseAuthorityYear="1848" box="[1129,1429,1986,2012]" class="Insecta" family="Sarcophagidae" genus="Mesomelena" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="193" pageNumber="194" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mesomelaena">
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FF0CFF6A5C77F84FFA2666A5" box="[1129,1429,1986,2012]" italics="true" pageId="193" pageNumber="194">Mesomelena mesomelaena</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The 
<typeStatus id="3F718814FF0FFF6958E2FF1AFE9F61C8" box="[252,300,151,177]" pageId="194" pageNumber="195">type</typeStatus>
material of this latter species should be in Loew’s collection in the MNHUB. In Loew’s collection under the label 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FF0FFF695968FF36FDC161AC" authorityName="Loew" authorityYear="1848" box="[374,626,187,213]" class="Insecta" family="Sarcophagidae" genus="Metopia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="194" pageNumber="195" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mesomelaena">
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FF0FFF695968FF36FDC161AC" box="[374,626,187,213]" italics="true" pageId="194" pageNumber="195">Metopia mesomelaena</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
there is only 
<specimenCount id="F6CCFD3FFF0FFF695B13FF36FC3A61AC" box="[781,905,187,213]" pageId="194" pageNumber="195" type="female">one female</specimenCount>
(in good condition) (J. Pohl, pers. comm., 
<date id="94741076FF0FFF695D73FF36FEB26180" pageId="194" pageNumber="195" value="2020-07">July 2020</date>
) which cannot be the 
<typeStatus id="3F718814FF0FFF6959EDFF52FD906180" box="[499,547,223,249]" pageId="194" pageNumber="195">type</typeStatus>
because 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF0FFF695A96FF52FCE26180" author="Loew, H." box="[648,849,223,249]" pageId="194" pageNumber="195" pagination="377 - 378" refId="ref356490" refString="Loew, H. (1848) Eine neue europaische Art der Gattung Metopia. Entomologische Zeitung, 9, 377 - 378." type="journal article" year="1848">Loew (1848: 378)</bibRefCitation>
stated that the single female of his collection had the abdomen destroyed. Under the name 
